TO HONOUR
A VERY SPECIAL FRIENDSHIP
WITH
"RAY" BENNETT (R.V.B.I.)

THOMAS WILLIAM KNIGHT (TK MAX)
ONE MORE ANGEL IN HEAVEN
ONE MORE STAR IN THE SKY
Love You Forever MUMMY & DADDY

PATRICK KNIGHT
20.12.44 TO 12.6.2014
MUCH LOVED HUSBAND, FATHER
BROTHER & UNCLE"Č
