╚1938 IN LOVING MEMORY OF ROGER D HAYNES 2012


Baby Grace
It broke our hearts to lose you
But you didn't go alone
Part of us went with you
The day God took you home
Love you forever, Mummy and Daddy xx

Be Still, Close Your Eyes, Breathe
Listen For My Footfall In Your Hearts
I Am Not Gone But Merely Walk Within You"ž
šIn Loving Memory of
Rev. Roy Victor Bagley
12.8.33 ~ 29.1.14
Softly the leaves of memory fall,
Gently I gather and treasure then all,
Unseen, unheard,
You are always near,
So missed, So loved, So very dear."¶
